<h1>Modular Extension - HMVC</h1>
<p><a href="https://bitbucket.org/wiredesignz/codeigniter-modular-extensions-hmvc/wiki/Home" target="_blank">Modular Extensions - HMVC</a>, developed by <a href="http://codeigniter.com/forums/member/39666/" target="_blank">wiredesignz</a>, 
extends CodeIgniter to allow for module  development. The CodeIgniter libraries <dfn>Loader</dfn>, <dfn>Router</dfn>, <dfn>Config</dfn> and <dfn>Language</dfn>
are either overwritten or extended to allow for module development and are located in the <dfn>application/third_party/MX/</dfn> folder.
</p>